A webhook lets your bot to answer commands issued from telegram chats and buttons inside messages  through an artisan command     php   artisan   telegraph:set-webhook   {bot_id}
the   bot_id  argument is mandatory if you have created more than one bot  programmatically  A webhook can be created programmatically for a bot by calling its   registerWebhook()  method     /**   @var   TelegraphBot   $bot */
 $bot  ->  registerWebhook  ()  ->  send  ();
