by setting buttons width  A button relative width can be set using a float number the total width percentage to be taken. Buttons will flow through the rows according to their width  this example would define two buttons on the first row and a large button on the second one:     use   DefStudio\Telegraph\Keyboard\ReplyKeyboard  ;

